 Andriy Popov via 123RFBoasting the latest technology, the Call Centre complete with&nbsp;embedded data security measures to protect customer information and identity,&nbsp;has been designed to offer Tigo customers dedicated world-class service. &nbsp; Migrating from E1 to the latest in Call Centre technology - the Session Initiation Protocol (SIP), allows for wide range of functionality and agility necessary to service Tigo&rsquo;s 10 million-strong customer base.